<p class="">I am not speaking about the reversal of that policy; I am pointing out how desirable it is, in deciding on policy abroad, that we should have in mind the potential financial power of this country.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-ad12ed8f-b7de-4dfd-84c5-5a746f2fa304" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
