<div class="content-item" id="contribution-b48a16fb-40fe-42a9-8dc3-5c73ccadcb0e">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-b48a16fb-40fe-42a9-8dc3-5c73ccadcb0e">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-b48a16fb-40fe-42a9-8dc3-5c73ccadcb0e">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-b48a16fb-40fe-42a9-8dc3-5c73ccadcb0e">
                Mr. Bevan
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-b48a16fb-40fe-42a9-8dc3-5c73ccadcb0e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1953-04-20/debates/128f6f27-3f7d-4810-b566-2a1a26ef5dcb/BudgetProposals#contribution-b48a16fb-40fe-42a9-8dc3-5c73ccadcb0e">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I did not say that. I do not want to interrupt too much, but I hope the hon. Member is clear now: I believe in stimulating demand for the right sort of investment.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-b48a16fb-40fe-42a9-8dc3-5c73ccadcb0e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
