<p class="">Would the hon. Member apply that also to the agricultural industry, which labour is leaving and which this year has 23,000 fewer workers? What is the incentive for workers to go back into agriculture?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
