<p class="">Order. Interventions should not develop into speeches.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-0c6956ad-8cdc-4cef-a455-71073b913c6e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1953-04-20/debates/128f6f27-3f7d-4810-b566-2a1a26ef5dcb/BudgetProposals#contribution-0c6956ad-8cdc-4cef-a455-71073b913c6e">
