            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-af431313-f1d0-416c-9e8d-ca69edcc2c4c">
                Mr. Bevan
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-af431313-f1d0-416c-9e8d-ca69edcc2c4c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1953-04-20/debates/128f6f27-3f7d-4810-b566-2a1a26ef5dcb/BudgetProposals#contribution-af431313-f1d0-416c-9e8d-ca69edcc2c4c">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">These were all facts within the control of the right hon. Gentleman. We cannot understand how he can pursue a credit policy which is bound to have the result of slight deflation in industry and at the same time expect industry to be sufficiently buoyant to give him increased revenue. How can he expect those two opposite things to operate together?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-af431313-f1d0-416c-9e8d-ca69edcc2c4c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1953-04-20/debates/128f6f27-3f7d-4810-b566-2a1a26ef5dcb/BudgetProposals#contribution-af431313-f1d0-416c-9e8d-ca69edcc2c4c">
