            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-bbd7eb6e-7ab4-403e-9bcf-f2cd6d7a986e">
                Mr. Herbert Morrison  (Lewisham, South)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-bbd7eb6e-7ab4-403e-9bcf-f2cd6d7a986e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
